downloadTitle: Skype for Business Mobile for Windows Phone
downloadDescription: Skype for Business for Windows Phone is an app that brings Skype for Business meetings, presence, instant messaging (IM), voice, and video capabilities to your mobile device. This guide provides detailed instructions on how to get started using Skype for Business Mobile for Windows Phone.
